TITLE: Creating Paginator with Custom Criteria and Sorting in Sylius
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a paginated collection with specific criteria and sorting options. It shows how to filter resources and sort them in a particular order while maintaining pagination functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-book/architecture/resource-layer.md#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
