TITLE: Implementing Custom Catalog Promotion Action in PHP for Sylius
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create a custom catalog promotion action class in Sylius. It includes the implementation of the CatalogPromotionActionInterface and shows how to apply the action to catalog items.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-cookbook-2.0/how-to-add-a-custom-catalog-promotion-action.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Promotion\Action;

use Sylius\Component\Core\Model\ChannelPricingInterface;
use Sylius\Component\Promotion\Model\CatalogPromotionActionInterface;

final class CustomAction implements CatalogPromotionActionInterface
{
    public function execute(ChannelPricingInterface $channelPricing, array $context = []): int
    {
        $appliedPromotion = $channelPricing->getAppliedPromotions();
        if (!$appliedPromotion->isEmpty()) {
            return 0;
        }

        $originalPrice = $channelPricing->getPrice();
        $result = (int) round($originalPrice * 0.9);

        return $originalPrice - $result;
    }

    public function getActionType(): string
    {
        return 'custom_action';
    }
}
```

