TITLE: Configuring Transitions with Symfony Workflow in Sylius
DESCRIPTION: This YAML configuration defines the 'address' transition for the Order Checkout workflow using Symfony Workflow. It specifies the possible source states and the target state for the transition.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-book/architecture/state-machine.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

