TITLE: Creating Custom Cart Promotion Rule Checker in PHP for Sylius
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a custom cart promotion rule checker class called 'HasTaxonRule'. It implements the RuleCheckerInterface and checks if the cart contains products from a specific taxon.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-cookbook-2.0/how-to-add-a-custom-cart-promotion-rule.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Promotion\Rule;

use Sylius\Component\Core\Model\OrderInterface;
use Sylius\Component\Core\Model\OrderItemInterface;
use Sylius\Component\Promotion\Checker\Rule\RuleCheckerInterface;

final class HasTaxonRule implements RuleCheckerInterface
{
    public const TYPE = 'has_taxon';

    public function isEligible(OrderInterface $subject, array $configuration): bool
    {
        $taxon = $configuration['taxon'];

        /** @var OrderItemInterface $item */
        foreach ($subject->getItems() as $item) {
            if ($item->getProduct()->hasTaxon($taxon)) {
                return true;
            }
        }

        return false;
    }
}
```

