TITLE: Custom Repository Method for Finding Products by Taxon in Sylius
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of a custom repository method that extends the base product repository to find products by a specific taxon.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-book/products/product-associations.md#2025-04-21_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Sylius\Bundle\CoreBundle\Doctrine\ORM\ProductRepository as BaseProductRepository;

class ProductRepository extends BaseProductRepository
{
    public function findByTaxon(Taxon $taxon): array
    {
        return $this->createQueryBuilder('p')
            ->join('p.productTaxons', 'pt')
            ->where('pt.taxon = :taxon')
            ->setParameter('taxon', $taxon)
            ->getQuery()
            ->getResult()
         ;
    }
}
```

