TITLE: Implementing Capture Payment Request Command Provider in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Creates a class to provide the capture payment request command based on the payment request action.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sylius/sylius/blob/2.1/docs/the-customization-guide/customizing-payments/how-to-integrate-a-payment-gateway-as-a-plugin.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace Acme\SyliusExamplePlugin\CommandProvider;

use Acme\SyliusExamplePlugin\Command\CapturePaymentRequest;
use Sylius\Bundle\PaymentBundle\CommandProvider\PaymentRequestCommandProviderInterface;
use Sylius\Component\Payment\Model\PaymentRequestInterface;

final readonly class CapturePaymentRequestCommandProvider implements PaymentRequestCommandProviderInterface
{
    public function supports(PaymentRequestInterface $paymentRequest): bool
    {
        return $paymentRequest->getAction() === PaymentRequestInterface::ACTION_CAPTURE;
    }

    public function provide(PaymentRequestInterface $paymentRequest): object
    {
        return new CapturePaymentRequest($paymentRequest->getId());
    }
}
```

