TITLE: Configuring Channel and Shop User Fixtures with Customer Pools in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML configuration demonstrates how to assign a specific customer pool during channel or shop customer creation in fixtures. It includes settings for a mobile channel and a shop user, both associated with the 'default' customer pool.
