TITLE: Hooks Prefixing in Twig Template
DESCRIPTION: This Twig code snippet demonstrates the manual control of hook name prefixing. The `_prefixes` parameter allows setting the hook name explicitly without merging ancestor's names. Here, the `hook_name` is prefixed with `custom_prefix_not_related_with_a_parent`.
